{"tid":2177144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"伍健偉入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-08-27T13:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T13:39:31.000Z","uid":19726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62e72e3b657f86f52c514de0b721df8ef4726a36","tid":2177144,"uid":19726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"你課金，我用晒所有Facebook account like你個page又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bzu1k1G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzu1k1G.jpg&h=13da1ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107497907250794/posts/320024552664794/?extid=o4LRznT2HN6vcdHu&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107497907250794%2Fposts%2F320024552664794%2F%3Fextid%3Do4LRznT2HN6vcdHu%26d%3Dn&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=98584857\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107497907250794/posts/320024552664794/?extid=o4LRznT2HN6vcdHu&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【我都好嬲好嬲】<br />\n如果「俾Like」等於「儲子彈」，咁「俾錢」等於乜？<br />\n係等於「幫手足」呀！<br />\n<br />\n見有手足一人一like撐香港，Carmen 同 鄭文杰議員 JC 發起一人一蚊撐手足！一人捐最少一蚊俾你認為可信嘅組織，影個捐款記錄嚟，如果一個星期內（9月4日 23:59 前）籌唔到多過鄭月娥月薪（43.4萬），我哋唔會辭職！但我哋將連續一個月巡迴到全港各區開早站！呼籲香港人捐錢撐手足！<br />\n<br />\n影個捐款記錄俾我哋！記得遮名遮個人資料：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/9QCResbEhrWXR8pj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F9QCResbEhrWXR8pj8&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b0cc6a20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/9QCResbEhrWXR8pj8</a><br />\n（如果開唔到嘅話inbox俾我都得！）<br />\n<br />\n#來吧香港人 #係考驗智慧嘅時候了<br />\n-----------------------<br />\n唔知捐邊好？（持續更新中）<br />\n1. 612人道支援基金<br />\n（提供醫療、刑事/民事法律費用、緊急經濟援助等）<br />\n<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=f844c6f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/</a><br />\n捐款網址：<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/zh/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fzh%2Fdonate&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=c36bfa37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/zh/donate</a><br />\n匯豐銀行：652-255761-001<br />\n轉數快：3261476<br />\n<br />\n2. 星火同盟（提供被捕保釋及有關法律諮詢、被捕者上庭出入護送及緊急醫療資助、探訪及援助在囚人士及其家屬）<br />\n以禮品卡形式捐款<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ourhkworks.com/product/giftcard/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourhkworks.com%2Fproduct%2Fgiftcard%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4be4c241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ourhkworks.com/product/giftcard/</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 民權觀察（提供法律支援）<br />\n捐款網頁：<a href=\"https://www.hkcro.org/fundraising/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcro.org%2Ffundraising%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=f316eb32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcro.org/fundraising/</a><br />\n上海商業銀行 328-82-58581-5，CIVIC INCUBATOR LIMITED<br />\n轉數快：0124636<br />\n<br />\n4. 好鄰舍北區教會（守護孩子行動）<br />\n<a href=\"https://goodneighbournd.wordpress.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoodneighbournd.wordpress.com%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=0bb5b536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goodneighbournd.wordpress.com/</a><br />\n包括「青少年醫肚計劃」「青少年幹事」「未來協助青年人項目」等項目<br />\n匯豐銀行 456-826650-001<br />\n請把入數紙電郵至goodneighbournd@gmail.com，請必需註明奉獻用途「自由分配」/「支援青少年幹事」<br />\n<br />\n5. 蘋果日報慈善基金<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk-charity.nextmedia.com/site/index.php?fuseaction=site.donationArea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk-charity.nextmedia.com%2Fsite%2Findex.php%3Ffuseaction%3Dsite.donationArea&d=Bx